---
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro';
---

<section id="timeline" class="bg-background py-[80px]">
  <Container class="max-w-[1000px]">
    <h2 class="text-[40px] font-serif font-semibold text-foreground text-center mb-16">How we got here.</h2>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- 1980s -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-primary">1980s</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-[8px] border border-border p-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">The beginning.</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Greenlawn Homes was founded as a family operation in Central Ohio, with a simple belief: manufactured homes could be a real path to homeownership for working families.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 1990s -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-primary">1990s</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-[8px] border border-border p-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Building communities.</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Through the 90s, we expanded from selling homes to owning and operating communities — giving us the ability to stand behind our residents long after the sale.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2000s -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-primary">2000s</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-[8px] border border-border p-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Growing the portfolio.</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We added communities across Central Ohio, from established neighborhoods to rural retreats, always with the same family-run approach.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2010s -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-primary">2010s</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-[8px] border border-border p-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Doubling down on quality.</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We became a proud dealer of Redman Homes and Adventure Homes, giving our buyers access to the best manufactured home brands in the country.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Today -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-primary">Today</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-[8px] border border-border p-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Nine communities, one family.</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Today, Greenlawn operates nine communities and has helped over 2,000 families find a home. We still run it the same way we always have — by knowing our residents and standing behind what we sell.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
